nodes.name: multi_task
nodes.class_name:
MKDTI(
  (entity_embedding): EmbeddingLayer(
    (embedding): Embedding(97238, 128)
  )
  (rgcn_layers): ModuleList(
    (0): EmbeddingLayer(
      (embedding): Embedding(97238, 128)
    )
    (1): RelGraphConv(
      (dropout): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    )
  )
  (shared_units): ModuleList(
    (0): AttentionUnit(
      (MLP_dti): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=128, bias=True)
      (MLP_cpi): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=128, bias=True)
    )
  )
  (drug_gcn): ModuleList(
    (0): GraphConv(in=78, out=128, normalization=both, activation=None)
    (1): GraphConv(in=128, out=128, normalization=both, activation=None)
  )
  (drug_output_layer): MLPNodeReadout(
    (in_project): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
    (activation): ReLU()
    (out_project): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
  )
  (compound_fc_layers): ModuleList(
    (0): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
    (1): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
  )
  (embed_protein): Embedding(8000, 128)
  (target_cnn): ModuleList(
    (0): Conv1d(128, 96, kernel_size=(3,), stride=(1,), padding=(1,))
    (1): Conv1d(96, 128, kernel_size=(3,), stride=(1,), padding=(1,))
    (2): Conv1d(128, 128, kernel_size=(3,), stride=(1,), padding=(1,))
  )
  (fc_layers): ModuleList(
    (0): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=256, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    (3): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=256, bias=True)
    (4): ReLU()
    (5): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    (6): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=1, bias=True)
  )
  (dti_fc_layers): ModuleList(
    (0): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=256, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    (3): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=1, bias=True)
  )
)
